summary: Yet another Wood Elf, seems like national Wood Elf day.  LOL
descriptionHtml:
Wood Elf, \"Aeron\"
  
Aeron pronounced ae-ron as a girl\'s name, also used as boy\'s name, is of Welsh origin, and the meaning of Aeron is \"battle\". The name of the ancient Celtic goddess of battle and slaughter.  It can also be referred to by the old Celtic kingdom of Aeron meaning \"North\".
  
Level 3 save game just finished the Golden claw quest, early in game. Heading back to Riverwood to find the claws owner.  If you like the look of her please download and enjoy.  Thanks.

Mods used for this save game. Face, body and some items may differ or be missing if you do not use the mods listed below. ( Bonus Kantana sword & Bows in the save ) All the mods listed below can be found here on Nexus. A big thank you to each everyone of their creators.

Extended_Slider_Colors
Better_Females_by_Bella
Then add bella Less_Make_up_Version
